description.en:
Our Generation Tea For Two teen doll accessories

Serve up hours of delectable fun with Tea for Two, the perfect miniature tea party set for teen dolls! Because drinking tea alone is wonderful, but in pairs it's even more fun. The set includes a teapot, cups and saucers, a sugar bowl with sugar cubes, cookies, candies, jam and more.

Mit Tea for Two, dem perfekten Miniatur-Teeparty-Set für Puppen im Teenageralter, kannst du stundenlangen, köstlichen Spaß haben!
